#. <section class="sutta" id="an6.36"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an6.36:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 6"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an6.36:0.2"
msgid "4. devatāvagga"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an6.36:0.3"
msgid "36. Vivādamūlasutta"
msgstr ""

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli3.335"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an6.36:1.1"
msgid "“Chayimāni, bhikkhave, vivādamūlāni."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an6.36:1.2"
msgid "Katamāni cha?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an6.36:1.3"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu kodhano hoti upanāhī."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an6.36:1.4"
msgid ""
"Yo so, bhikkhave, bhikkhu kodhano hoti upanāhī so sattharipi agāravo "
"viharati appatisso, dhammepi agāravo viharati appatisso, saṃghepi agāravo "
"viharati appatisso, sikkhāyapi na paripūrakārī hoti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an6.36:1.5"
msgid ""
"Yo so, bhikkhave, bhikkhu satthari agāravo viharati appatisso, dhamme "
"agāravo viharati appatisso, saṃghe agāravo viharati appatisso, sikkhāya na "
"paripūrakārī so saṃghe vivādaṃ janeti, yo hoti vivādo bahujanāhitāya "
"bahujanāsukhāya bahuno janassa anatthāya ahitāya dukkhāya devamanussānaṃ."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an6.36:1.6"
msgid ""
"Evarūpañce tumhe, bhikkhave, vivādamūlaṃ ajjhattaṃ vā bahiddhā vā "
"samanupasseyyātha. Tatra tumhe, bhikkhave, tasseva pāpakassa vivādamūlassa "
"pahānāya vāyameyyātha."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an6.36:1.7"
msgid ""
"Evarūpañce tumhe, bhikkhave, vivādamūlaṃ ajjhattaṃ vā bahiddhā vā na "
"samanupasseyyātha, tatra tumhe, bhikkhave, tasseva pāpakassa vivādamūlassa "
"āyatiṃ anavassavāya paṭipajjeyyātha."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an6.36:1.8"
msgid ""
"Evametassa pāpakassa vivādamūlassa pahānaṃ hoti. Evametassa pāpakassa "
"vivādamūlassa āyatiṃ anavassavo hoti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an6.36:2.1"
msgid "Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, bhikkhu makkhī hoti paḷāsī … pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an6.36:2.2"
msgid "issukī hoti maccharī …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an6.36:2.3"
msgid "saṭho hoti māyāvī …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an6.36:2.4"
msgid "pāpiccho hoti micchādiṭṭhi …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an6.36:2.5"
msgid "sandiṭṭhiparāmāsī hoti ādhānaggāhī duppaṭinissaggī."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an6.36:2.6"
msgid ""
"Yo so, bhikkhave, bhikkhu sandiṭṭhiparāmāsī hoti ādhānaggāhī "
"duppaṭinissaggī, so sattharipi agāravo viharati appatisso, dhammepi agāravo "
"viharati appatisso, saṅghepi agāravo viharati appatisso, sikkhāyapi na "
"paripūrakārī hoti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an6.36:2.7"
msgid ""
"Yo so, bhikkhave, bhikkhu satthari agāravo viharati appatisso, dhamme … "
"saṅghe agāravo viharati appatisso, sikkhāya na paripūrakārī, so saṅghe "
"vivādaṃ janeti, yo hoti vivādo bahujanāhitāya bahujanāsukhāya bahuno janassa "
"anatthāya ahitāya dukkhāya devamanussānaṃ."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an6.36:2.8"
msgid ""
"Evarūpañce tumhe, bhikkhave, vivādamūlaṃ ajjhattaṃ vā bahiddhā vā "
"samanupasseyyātha. Tatra tumhe, bhikkhave, tasseva pāpakassa vivādamūlassa "
"pahānāya vāyameyyātha."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an6.36:2.9"
msgid ""
"Evarūpañce tumhe, bhikkhave, vivādamūlaṃ ajjhattaṃ vā bahiddhā vā na "
"samanupasseyyātha. Tatra tumhe, bhikkhave, tasseva pāpakassa vivādamūlassa "
"āyatiṃ anavassavāya paṭipajjeyyātha."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an6.36:2.10"
msgid ""
"Evametassa pāpakassa vivādamūlassa pahānaṃ hoti. Evametassa pāpakassa "
"vivādamūlassa āyatiṃ anavassavo hoti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an6.36:2.11"
msgid "Imāni kho, bhikkhave, cha vivādamūlānī”ti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an6.36:2.12"
msgid "Chaṭṭhaṃ."
msgstr ""
